context: <user> Can you find me a cheap guesthouse to stay at? <system> We have nine cheap guest houses. All offer free internet and free parking. Some have 0 star ratings and others have 4 stars. What sounds good to you? <user> Great, I want one with 4 Stars. <system> There are several that meet that criteria. I can recommend the Autumn House in the East of the city. <user> Sure. Please book a reservation for two people, Saturday, two nights. <system> Autumn House is full. Can I try to reserve one of the other ones for you? <user> Yes, try another place as long as it is still in the cheap price range. <system> How about allenbell? Your reference number is 2SUPQQPL .<user> That will work,thank you for booking it,goodbye. <system>
